  "_comment_google": "Google Workspace agent (read-only). Create an OAuth 'Desktop app' client in Google Cloud, paste the id+secret, then run `goon google auth` to fill the refresh token. Set GOOGLE_CLOUD_PROJECT to enable log search. Guide: docs/google-workspace.md",
